  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2006-07-13",
    "date": "2006-09-14T21:04:26Z",
    "text": "Recycling Investment Saves Energy or the RISE Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow a taxpayer election of a tax credit for 15% of the cost of qualified reuse and recycling property or a tax deduction for 50% of the adjusted basis of such property; and (2) define solid waste disposal facilities to include reuse and recycling functions for purposes of tax-exempt bond financing."
